com.amazon.inapp.purchasing

Class GetUserIdResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazon.inapp.purchasing.GetUserIdResponse

  • public final class GetUserIdResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the result of a call to PurchasingManager.initiateGetUserIdRequest(). It is sent asynchronously to the registered PurchasingObserver via PurchasingObserver.onGetUserIdResponse(GetUserIdResponse).
